				IfEqual, Ctrl2Add, CheckBox, SetEnv, CtrlName, Button
				IfEqual, Ctrl2Add, GroupBox, SetEnv, CtrlName, Button
				IfEqual, Ctrl2Add, Hotkey, SetEnv, CtrlName, msctls_hotkey32
